    <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
      <span class="apn-hydr-label">Hydration MasterClass</span>
      <h1 class="apn-hydr-h1">Close Your Hydration Gap.</h1>
      <div style="width:64px;height:3px;background:#06A5C5;margin:20px auto 28px;"></div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#9CA3AF;line-height:1.6;">
          Welcome back, <strong id="apn-hydr-name-display" style="color:#F8FAFB;"></strong>.
          Your Hydration score: <strong id="apn-hydr-score-display" style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:20px;"></strong>/100.
        </p>
        <div id="apn-hydr-tier-badge" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:12px;padding:6px 18px;border-radius:3px;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;"></div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-size:18px;color:#9CA3AF;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.65;">
        30 minutes of the most specific coaching you will read on hydration performance. Evidence-based. Tier-matched to where you are right now.
      </p>

      <div style="text-align:left;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 40px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-radius:4px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;color:#06A5C5;margin-bottom:16px;">What you will cover</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;">
          <li style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#9CA3AF;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span>Module 1 — Your Gap Report</span><span style="color:#6B7280;">2 min</span></li>
          <li style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#9CA3AF;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span>Module 2 — Why This Costs You</span><span style="color:#6B7280;">5 min</span></li>
          <li style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#9CA3AF;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span>Module 3 — The Diagnosis</span><span style="color:#6B7280;">5 min</span></li>
          <li style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#9CA3AF;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><span>Module 4 — The 30-Day Protocol</span><span style="color:#6B7280;">10 min</span></li>
