      <a href="#apn-hydr-m1" style="display:inline-block;background:#06A5C5;color:#fff;font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;padding:16px 36px;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;">Start the MasterClass &#8595;</a>
