            <p class="apn-hydr-product-meta"><strong>1 serving (mixed in 20 oz of water) 60 to 90 minutes before training</strong> as your primary application. Can also be used intra-workout for sessions over 60 minutes (half serving in 16 oz) or post-training for replenishment (1 serving in 20 oz within 30 minutes of finishing).</p>
