            <p class="apn-hydr-product-meta">Replenish combined with Recharge (Creatine) produces a compound hydration effect: extracellular hydration from electrolytes plus intracellular hydration from creatine-mediated water retention in muscle cells. The two mechanisms operate on different compartments and reinforce each other.</p>
