          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="apn-tier-block-h" data-tier="elite" style="display:block;">
        <div class="apn-hydr-product-card">
          <p class="apn-hydr-product-label">Advanced Product (Elite Tier)</p>
          <h3 class="apn-hydr-product-name">Replenish Plus</h3>
          <p class="apn-hydr-product-price">$44.99</p>
          <p class="apn-hydr-product-desc">At Elite tier, Replenish Plus is the precision tool. Creatine saturation combined with full electrolyte replacement creates a hydration environment that maximizes both plasma volume and intracellular water retention simultaneously.</p>
        </div>
